data.description: Move-in ready 1,400 square foot brick Ranch now available in Elyria. Built in 1964, this home comes with a 725 sq ft half-finished basement/in-law suite, complete with bed, kitchen, bathroom, and living room. Sitting on a .48 acre corner lot, fully fenced in the backyard, this home also includes a large 2 car attached garage. The home features a brand-new paint job, new floors, and other useful updates. Additional unique features include a 3 seasons room with lots of natural light, easy highway access, and a short 4-mile trip to downtown Elyria. Call for your showing today.
